dc_description_s: This point data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Manitowoc County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Manitowoc_PLSS_2018.gdb. [Infomation on each Public Land Survey System (PLSS) standard corner in Manitowoc County is stored in this feature class. Corner points are identified and indexed by the state standard NWisconsin Corner Point Identification System.N]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
